args:
Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: I will not cut one penny from Social Security or Medicare, and I will not raise the retirement age by one day. I kept that promise for 4 years, and I will keep it again. By contrast, Kamala Harris cast the tie-breaking vote to cut Medicare by $237 billion dollars—a heartless betrayal of American seniors!
